= Research Analyst Roles in Long-Only Equity Fund Managers

== Overview

Research Analysts form the analytical backbone of long-only equity fund managers, responsible for generating investment ideas, conducting deep fundamental research, and providing recommendations to Portfolio Managers. In Australia, these roles exist across both boutique fund managers (e.g., Magellan Financial Group, Platinum Asset Management) and the Australian divisions of global managers (e.g., Fidelity, T. Rowe Price, Schroders).

