*5:00pm - 6:30pm*: Finish draft investment paper on Domino's. Create summary presentation for next week's Investment Committee. Send to senior analyst for first review before submitting to Portfolio Manager.

*Evening*: Most evenings finish by 6:30-7:00pm. Occasionally stay later during reporting season or when finalising investment papers. Take home reading – annual reports, industry white papers, broker research.

=== Career Progression Pathways
- *Within 2-3 years*: Promotion to Senior Analyst, increased responsibility for larger/more complex stocks
- *Alternative internal moves*: Specialist roles (ESG analyst, quantitative researcher)
- *External opportunities*: 
  - Larger fund manager (access to bigger companies, different investment style)
  - Hedge fund (event-driven, long/short equity)
  - Private equity (fundamental research skills translate well)

