== Australian Market Context

=== Regulatory Considerations for Research Analysts

*ASIC Market Conduct Requirements:*
- Research must be objective, based on reasonable grounds
- Clear separation between research and corporate finance (Chinese walls)
- Disclosure of conflicts of interest
- Personal trading restrictions and pre-clearance requirements

*Insider Trading Restrictions:*
- Strict protocols when receiving material non-public information (MNPI)
- Blackout periods around results announcements for covered stocks
- Prohibition on trading ahead of research report publication

*Continuous Disclosure (ASX Listing Rules):*
- Understanding of what constitutes material information
- Recognition when company may be in breach of disclosure obligations
- Protocols for handling selective disclosure situations

